                "title": "Escrime de Favonius"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Compétence élémentaire</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Inflige 3 pts de</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">DGT Anémo</span> <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">et bascule de force la cible pour le personnage suivant.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/16/35653081/f21a21302c39df14caac1bbc0a6bef40_4348620680429987834.png",
                "id": "talent66509",
                "key": "Épée de tourbillon",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Épée de tourbillon"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Déchaînement élémentaire</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Soigne tous vos personnages pour 2 pts et invoque un </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">champ de pissenlits</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/16/35653081/06d120531fd7d61a928bac235bbaeed2_5380787419088139398.png",
                "id": "talent49250",
                "key": "Brise de pissenlit",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Brise de pissenlit"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Invocation</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Phase finale </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">: Inflige 2 pts de </span><span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">DGT Anémo</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> et soigne votre personnage actif pour 1 pt.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nombre d'utilisation :</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/16/35653081/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_8581981500015522683.png",
                "id": "talent26645",
                "key": "Champ de pissenlits",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/16/35653081/9138f4f0e38e85d3c4e035bdf2025636_5664200415132208144.png",
                "title": "Champ de pissenlits"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Réagit avec les éléments déjà appliqués pour les réactions élémentaires :</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anémo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Dispersion Cryo </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">: Inflige 1 pt de DGT Cryo à tous les personnages adverses autres que la cible</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anémo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Dispersion Hydro </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">: Inflige 1 pt de DGT Hydro à tous les personnages adverses autres que la cible</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anémo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Dispersion Pyro </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">: Inflige 1 pt de DGT Pyro à tous les personnages adverses autres que la cible</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anémo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Électro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Dispersion </span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Électro </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">: Inflige 1 pt de DGT Électro à tous les personnages adverses autres que la cible</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/16/35653081/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_1235379237724929116.png",
                "id": "talent11396",
                "key": "DGT Anémo",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "DGT Anémo"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">DGT physiques</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Les DGT physiques n'appliquent aucun élément et ne peuvent pas non plus déclencher de réactions élémentaires.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Nombre d'utilisation</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Après le déclenchement de l'effet de cette carte, 1 de ses </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">utilisations </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">est consommée.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Une carte est immédiatement défaussée une fois toutes ses </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">utilisations </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">épuisées.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/16/35653081/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_1869472786721779386.png",
